279
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:11,279
...we’re just demon slayers who walk the world.

280
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:12,239
Demon slayers?

281
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,240
Demon slayers?

282
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:14,599
You originally...

283
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:16,999
...should have been the King of East宁.

284
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,239
Isn’t that the same?

285
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:19,719
Zhuang Sheng...

286
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,039
What?

287
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:29,559
Charge!

288
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:37,799
Even the King of East宁 is still a demon slayer.

289
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:39,599
According to my nature...

290
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,159
...even if I became a king...

291
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:44,039
...I’d probably still be running all over the world,
slaying demons and saving people.

292
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:46,919
Demon Slayer Meng Chuan...

293
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:49,999
Next, we’ll have to leave the Great Zhou Dynasty...

294
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,639
...and head to the Dayue Dynasty.

295
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:53,479
We’re going to reinforce Two Worlds Island.

296
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:54,999
Once we leave...

297
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,879
...who knows how long it’ll be before we return.

298
00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:13,759
Achuan...

299
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:14,639
Clan Leader...

300
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:15,519
Young Master!

301
00:16:15,520 --> 00:16:15,879
Young Master!

302
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:16,439
Qian Fang...

303
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,679
Meng Chuan...

304
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,439
You’re back!

305
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,439
Yeah.

306
00:16:23,640 --> 00:16:24,640
I’m back.

307
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,279
How have you been doing at the Meng family?

308
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:26,879
Xiao Ye...

309
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,279
The Meng family is great.

310
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:29,999
All the elder grandpas are doing well.

311
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,439
But...

312
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:42,039
...the newly arrived Jade Sun Palace Master
is not so good.

313
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,960
Giddy-up!

314
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:00,920
Giddy-up!

315
00:17:06,280 --> 00:17:07,280
Giddy-up!

316
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:19,280
Palace Master!

317
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:20,520
Palace Master!

318
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:23,359
Palace...

319
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:24,439
Palace Master!

320
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,399
How urgent is it...

321
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,599
...that you’re panting like this?

322
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,440
Meng Chuan...

323
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,640
...has returned.

324
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:33,239
Senior Brother has returned!

325
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,279
Meng Chuan...

326
00:17:53,379 --> 00:17:55,379
[Azalea/Yingshanhong — Evil Dragon Clan]

327
00:17:55,403 --> 00:18:43,952
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

